{"aid": "http://arxiv.org/abs/2504.02366v1", "title": "Non-Koszulness in a family of properads", "summary": "Proving Koszulness of a properad can be very hard, but sometimes one can look
at its Koszul complex to look for obstructions for Koszulness. In this paper,
we present a method and tools to prove non-Koszulness of many properads in a
family of quadratic properads. We illustrate this method on a family of
associative and coassociative properads with one quadratic compatibility
relation.", "main_category": "math.AT", "categories": "math.AT", "published": "2025-04-03T07:56:48Z"}
